A new video shared online has shown the moment the woman who accused Neymar of r*pe was seen assaulting the football star in a hotel room. The lady can be heard saying: ‘I’m going to hit you. Do you know why I’m going to hit you? Do you know why? Do you know why? Because you assaulted me yesterday. You left me here alone.’ This is coming after Neymar shared WhatsApp chats and video the woman sent him. A Twitter user, Mr. Alabi of Lagos who shared the video wrote: “Footage from the Neymar Brouhaha , after God, Fear Women.” Watch video below: Source